I really don't like the idea of building separate ROMs for NTSC and PAL, so I use a region detection system on startup and dynamically adapt all timing-critical sections.<br /><br />I don't necessarily adapt the speed at which the game runs because that introduces a lot of complications, but at least my programs run without glitches or any kind of weird behavior in any console.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Fri Apr 15, 2011 8:51 am</p><hr />
